{"tid":1127603,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"粉嶺「浪舍」懷疑虐待動物，場內如亂葬崗","createTime":"2019-04-27T08:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T08:31:26.000Z","uid":43678,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3cd2695e9406b5add55f561a615b8dfa2a57f7","tid":1127603,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:34:14.000Z","msg":"極緊急！粉嶺「浪舍」懷疑虐待動物　場內如亂葬崗　警方愛協到場<br />\n<br />\n【動物突發】打鼓嶺坪輋一個名為「浪舍」的狗場，被多名獨立義工揭發懷疑虐待動物，日前用航拍發現場內如亂葬崗般，環境惡劣。義工現在聯同警方及愛協到場調查，狗場負責人拒絕他們進入，目前仍在對峙中，警員已召CID到場，漁護署人員亦正趕來，或可強行破門入屋。<br />\n<br />\n義工施小姐對本報表示，她在半年前將兩狗交「浪舍」暫托，但對方一直不肯告訴他們地址和不准他們探狗，她發現很多獨立義工都是苦主，日前終掌握到該場地址，到場卻發現門外草叢有狗屍，翌日用航拍發現場內極惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n本報會繼續跟進事態發展，稍後會有詳細報道。<br />\n<br />\n#香港動物報 #狗 #粉嶺 #浪舍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFWAvUe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFWAvUe.png&h=25a50d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQzFG0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQzFG0U.png&h=344e9b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/(null)?metadata=vkPqBF34KF0hMc5rNGTRZ9tshw0fD6GI5MSY2q7mTAM3AVTiFRW2IJ3foKdDcW2gk9Cev72Hj0V2VOxpAn8Bwsni&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%28null%29%3Fmetadata%3DvkPqBF34KF0hMc5rNGTRZ9tshw0fD6GI5MSY2q7mTAM3AVTiFRW2IJ3foKdDcW2gk9Cev72Hj0V2VOxpAn8Bwsni%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7a1f2a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/(null)?metadata=vkPqBF34KF0hMc5rNGTRZ9tshw0fD6GI5MSY2q7mTAM3AVTiFRW2IJ3foKdDcW2gk9Cev72Hj0V2VOxpAn8Bwsni&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"10f66e288320131a74ad114c82091f7bc1da3a02","tid":1127603,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"打鼓嶺坪輋一個狗場懷疑發生虐待動物案。有狗義工發現坪輋一個狗場衞生環境差劣，有死去狗隻陳屍，沒有人理會，遂報警求助。今早(27日)10時許，警方及愛護動物協會人員抵達該個狗場調查，惟場主拒絕開門，一度對峙，漁護署人員亦到場協助。期間場內人士與電視台攝製隊人員爭吵時，毀壞器材。警員以涉嫌刑事毀壞將負責人拘捕，負責人事後表示不適。 <br />\n<br />\n有狗義工在facebook貼文及展示航拍圖片，並指「場內如亂葬崗般，環境惡劣」。場內有數十隻狗隻，但有狗屍遍地。案件暫列虐待動物案處理。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190427/mobile/bkn-20190427142432272-0427_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190427%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190427142432272-0427_00822_001.html&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=b473c544\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190427/mobile/bkn-20190427142432272-0427_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a5bc8b7ebb63a5a6e0304897011e9992b3159bab","tid":1127603,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:38:12.000Z","msg":"幫趁嗰啲人個腦有事？<br />\n<br />\n你會唔會送屋企人去個不知實際地址啲地方「暫托」"},{"pid":"e138dd9a3b41b23e28280cec7707aab1e8bed322","tid":1127603,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7008ddf184303ff128ef1d162a74872a0fdb7f77","tid":1127603,"uid":216477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T13:41:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4c64628cd70ef90ea78556d484445e941d84f3b","tid":1127603,"uid":43296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5256937863509a0aca20a8a9015c826a28609dc0","tid":1127603,"uid":7003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:11:17.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 依單野真係離曬譜"},{"pid":"aab3ab72557451300d3dd3312bd42af408f6de57","tid":1127603,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"死廢老"},{"pid":"12b4c139a57ae166274a125b9890b2a9263eaca0","tid":1127603,"uid":43296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}